# netM8 AI - SaaS Platform

This is the SaaS platform for netM8, a unified personal AI agent service. Built on a production-ready Next.js template designed to run on Cloudflare Workers with OpenNext, it provides the infrastructure for authentication, team management, billing, and multi-tenant features.

**Live Platform**: [netm8.com](mdc:https:/netm8.com)

**GitHub Repository**: [netM8_AI](mdc:https:/github.com/Jaketdaniels/netM8_AI.git)

## netM8 Service Overview

netM8 is a unified personal AI agent that provides secure and private access to your digital ecosystem. Users interact with a single AI agent for all their needs - from internet search and deep research to device management, entertainment, communications, and personal organization.

### Example Use Cases:
- **Research**: Internet search, deep research, data analysis
- **Technical**: Network settings, device troubleshooting, shortcuts and hacks
- **Organization**: Diary management, email management, task coordination
- **Communications**: Unified messaging (iMessage, SMS, WhatsApp, Messenger, Snapchat, Signal, Telegram)
- **Entertainment**: Spotify playlists, Plex library organization, content downloads
- **Life Management**: Shopping, finances, travel planning

## Platform Infrastructure

- **Authentication & Security**: Complete auth system with Lucia Auth, WebAuthn/Passkeys, OAuth, rate limiting, and session management
- **Multi-tenancy**: Teams/organizations with role-based permissions and tenant isolation
- **Billing System**: Credit-based billing with Stripe integration for AI usage tracking
- **Admin Dashboard**: User management, credit administration, and analytics
- **Modern Stack**: Next.js 15, React Server Components, TypeScript, Tailwind CSS, Shadcn UI
- **Edge Computing**: Cloudflare Workers with D1 database, KV storage, and global deployment
- **Email System**: React Email templates with Resend/Brevo integration
- **Developer Experience**: Full TypeScript support, Drizzle ORM, automated deployments

You are an expert in TypeScript, Node.js, Next.js App Router, React, Shadcn UI, Radix UI, Tailwind CSS and DrizzleORM.
